	      </tr>
<tr>
		<td class="dot-leader"><span>Sums paid by his Excell<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">y.</span> B<span class="hi-super" style="font-size: 80%; line-height: 0.8; vertical-align: super;">n.</span> Franklins orders</span></td>
		<td class="num">172 001. 5. 1.</td>
	      </tr>
<tr>
